WEBVTT

00:02.043 --> 00:04.175
Kate:
HER NAME'S KENDRA MURPHY.

00:04.175 --> 00:05.586
AT 3:00 A.M. THIS MORNING,

00:05.586 --> 00:07.888
SHE WALKED INTO A SWIFT-MART
WITH A LIVE GRENADE

00:07.888 --> 00:09.720
AND DEMANDED
A PACK OF CIGARETTES.

00:09.720 --> 00:11.972
THE CLERK WAS TERRIFIED.

00:11.972 --> 00:14.185
HE GAVE HER THE SMOKES
AND RAN OUT OF THERE.

00:14.185 --> 00:16.807
SHE PULLED THE PIN,
BLEW THE PLACE SKY HIGH.

00:16.807 --> 00:19.060
WAS ANYBODY HURT?
NO, THANK GOD.

00:19.060 --> 00:20.981
WHERE ON EARTH
DID SHE GET A GRENADE?

00:20.981 --> 00:23.404
SHE TOOK HER THUMB
OUT OF HER MOUTH LONG ENOUGH

00:23.404 --> 00:25.736
TO GIVE ME HER NAME, RANK,
AND SERIAL NUMBER.

00:25.736 --> 00:27.318
LOOK AT THIS.

00:27.318 --> 00:30.651
SPECIALIST KENDRA MURPHY,
ILLINOIS NATIONAL GUARD.

00:30.651 --> 00:32.783
TWO TOURS OF DUTY
IN AFGHANISTAN.

00:32.783 --> 00:34.155
DID SHE SEE ANY COMBAT?

00:34.155 --> 00:36.827
YEAH,
YOU COULD SAY THAT.

00:36.827 --> 00:40.161
"PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES
AWARDS THE SILVER STAR

00:40.161 --> 00:41.832
"TO SPECIALIST KENDRA MURPHY

00:41.832 --> 00:44.545
FOR GALLANTRY IN ACTION
AGAINST AN ARMED ENEMY."

00:44.545 --> 00:46.427
SHE'S
A GENUINE WAR HERO.

00:46.427 --> 00:48.219
SHE RAN STRAIGHT INTO
ENEMY FIRE,

00:48.219 --> 00:50.261
BLEW UP A TALIBAN POSITION,

00:50.261 --> 00:51.932
THEN DRAGGED TWO SOLDIERS
OUT OF HARM'S WAY.

00:53.514 --> 00:55.306
EXTREME HYPERORALITY
COULD INDICATE

00:55.306 --> 00:57.438
DAMAGE
TO THE TEMPORAL LOBES.

00:57.438 --> 00:59.270
YEAH, I THOUGHT
MAYBE SHE'D SUFFERED

00:59.270 --> 01:01.061
SOME FORM OF
TRAUMATIC BRAIN INJURY,

01:01.061 --> 01:02.893
BUT ACCORDING TO
HER SERVICE RECORD,

01:02.893 --> 01:04.565
SHE DIDN'T GET
SO MUCH AS A SCRATCH.

01:04.565 --> 01:06.567
WELL, JUST 'CAUSE HER RECORD
DOESN'T SHOW IT

01:06.567 --> 01:08.569
DOESN'T MEAN SHE WASN'T
EXPOSED TO A BOMB BLAST
THAT RATTLED HER SKULL.

01:08.569 --> 01:10.241
THOUSANDS OF SOLDIERS
ARE COMING HOME

01:10.241 --> 01:11.492
WITH UNDIAGNOSED T.B.I.s.

01:11.492 --> 01:13.534
IT'S AN EPIDEMIC.

01:13.534 --> 01:15.035
DO YOU STILL KEEP
THAT BAG

01:15.035 --> 01:17.037
OF TOXIC REFINED-SUGAR PRODUCTS
AT YOUR DESK?

01:19.200 --> 01:22.373
GOT SOMETHING FOR YOU.

01:26.257 --> 01:29.380
OH, NO, YOU DON'T WANT --
DON'T -- YOU DON'T -- HERE.

01:29.380 --> 01:31.382
YOU DON'T WANT TO EAT THAT.

01:31.382 --> 01:33.384
LET ME GET
SOMETHING ELSE.

01:35.976 --> 01:38.889
FIRST, YOU HAVE TO
ANSWER A QUESTION.

01:38.889 --> 01:41.061
DO YOU KNOW
WHERE YOU ARE?

01:41.061 --> 01:42.102
IN JAIL.

01:42.102 --> 01:44.645
NOT EXACTLY, BUT...

01:44.645 --> 01:45.986
YOU ARE UNDER ARREST.

01:45.986 --> 01:48.149
DO YOU KNOW
WHY YOU'RE HERE?

01:48.149 --> 01:50.321
BECAUSE
I TOOK THE SMOKES.

01:53.654 --> 01:55.286
WEREN'T YOU WORRIED
THAT YOU'D GET HURT

01:55.286 --> 01:56.617
WHEN YOU SET OFF
THAT GRENADE?

01:56.617 --> 02:00.911
KENDRA,
WERE YOU AFRAID AT ALL?

02:00.911 --> 02:02.583
YOU ARE HOT.

02:04.505 --> 02:05.916
I GOT A MOTEL ROOM.

02:05.916 --> 02:07.168
YOU WANT TO
GET OUT OF HERE?

02:07.168 --> 02:08.919
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S APPROPRIATE.

02:08.919 --> 02:12.132
I, UH -- I REALLY WANT TO
HAVE SEX WITH YOU.

02:12.132 --> 02:14.805
IF YOU DON'T WANT TO
TALK TO ME NOW, I CAN
COME BACK LATER.

02:14.805 --> 02:16.927
WHY DON'T YOU
WANT TO HAVE SEX WITH ME?

02:18.429 --> 02:21.562
DON'T YOU THINK
I'M PRETTY?

02:28.028 --> 02:30.481
YOUR WIFE IS SUFFERING FROM
A NEUROBEHAVIORAL DISORDER

02:30.481 --> 02:32.773
KNOWN AS
KLUVER-BUCY SYNDROME.

02:32.773 --> 02:35.866
THE COMPULSIVE SEXUAL BEHAVIOR,
ORAL FIXATION,

02:35.866 --> 02:38.279
LACK OF FEAR, AND MOOD SWINGS
ARE ALL SYMPTOMS.

02:38.279 --> 02:39.780
HOW DID SHE GET IT?

02:39.780 --> 02:41.622
FROM A VIRUS THAT'S
CAUSING HER BRAIN TO SWELL.

02:41.622 --> 02:43.043
IT'S KNOWN AS
ENCEPHALITIS.

02:44.955 --> 02:46.707
BUT YOU CAN CURE HER,
RIGHT?

02:46.707 --> 02:52.503
THE ENCEPHALITIS WAS CAUSED BY
THE HERPES VIRUS, TYPE 2.

02:52.503 --> 02:54.174
THERE'S NO CURE,
BUT THERE ARE TREATMENTS.

02:54.174 --> 02:55.596
HERPES?

02:55.596 --> 02:57.678
SOMETIMES
IT CAN TRAVEL TO THE BRAIN.

02:57.678 --> 02:59.350
SHE'S ON ANTI-VIRALS,

02:59.350 --> 03:01.262
AND THE INFLAMMATION'S
ALREADY STARTED TO GO DOWN,

03:01.262 --> 03:02.563
SO THAT'S A GOOD SIGN.

03:02.563 --> 03:04.685
AND SHE'S ALSO
ON MOOD STABILIZERS

03:04.685 --> 03:06.767
FOR HER
BEHAVIORAL ISSUES.

03:06.767 --> 03:09.980
WHEN DID YOU FIRST NOTICE
YOUR WIFE ACTING STRANGELY?

03:09.980 --> 03:12.483
WHEN SHE FIRST
COMES BACK FROM THE WAR.

03:12.483 --> 03:14.194
SHE'S ALL SKITTISH.

03:14.194 --> 03:16.026
SHE JUMPS
IF I SO MUCH AS TOUCH HER.

03:16.026 --> 03:19.079
AND THEN
SHE STARTS GOING OUT AT NIGHT,

03:19.079 --> 03:22.162
SO I FOLLOW HER.

03:22.162 --> 03:24.034
SHE'S PICKING UP GUYS
IN BARS

03:24.034 --> 03:25.916
AND BANGING THEM
AT SOME SLEAZY MOTEL.

03:25.916 --> 03:29.710
I-I GUESS I SHOULDN'T BE
SURPRISED SHE CAUGHT HERPES.

03:29.710 --> 03:32.463
TO BE CLEAR,
I BELIEVE IT'S THE HERPES

03:32.463 --> 03:35.256
THAT CAUSED
YOUR WIFE'S HYPERSEXUALITY.

03:35.256 --> 03:36.887
SHE DIDN'T GET IT
FROM ME.

03:36.887 --> 03:40.641
WE WERE VIRGINS
WHEN WE GOT MARRIED.

03:40.641 --> 03:44.265
I WAS ALWAYS
FAITHFUL TO HER.

03:44.265 --> 03:46.767
I'VE TRIED TO CONVINCE HER
TO GET HELP,

03:46.767 --> 03:50.060
AND THEN ONE NIGHT
SHE GOES OUT...

03:50.060 --> 03:52.022
SHE NEVER COMES BACK.

03:52.022 --> 03:55.115
AND THAT WAS A MONTH AGO.

03:55.115 --> 03:57.488
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHO SHE IS ANYMORE.

03:58.909 --> 04:01.161
I JUST WANT MY WIFE BACK.

04:04.124 --> 04:06.667
YOU EXPECT ME
TO DROP THE CHARGES

04:06.667 --> 04:08.789
BECAUSE
SHE CAUGHT AN STD?

04:08.789 --> 04:10.461
KENDRA NEEDS
NEUROLOGICAL TREATMENT,

04:10.461 --> 04:11.582
NOT JAIL.

04:11.582 --> 04:13.253
LOOK,
IF YOU WERE COMING TO ME

04:13.253 --> 04:16.216
SAYING THAT SHE HAD BEEN
SHOT IN THE HEAD BY THE TALIBAN,

04:16.216 --> 04:19.380
THEN MAYBE I COULD JUSTIFY
DROPPING THE CHARGES, BUT --

04:19.380 --> 04:21.552
WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE
HOW SHE GOT SICK?

04:21.552 --> 04:22.883
SHE'S A DECORATED
WAR VET.

04:22.883 --> 04:24.515
I SPOKE TO HER OB/GYN.

04:24.515 --> 04:26.437
KENDRA WAS SCREENED FOR STDs
A WEEK BEFORE DEPLOYMENT.

04:26.437 --> 04:27.978
SHE TESTED NEGATIVE.

04:27.978 --> 04:30.811
SO, SHE OBVIOUSLY PICKED IT UP
IN AFGHANISTAN.

04:30.811 --> 04:33.394
[ SIGHS ]
MAYBE I COULD USE THAT.

04:33.394 --> 04:35.736
BUT SHE BLEW UP A
CONVENIENCE STORE
WITH A GRENADE.

04:35.736 --> 04:37.568
I WOULD BE GOING
WAY OUT ON A LIMB.

04:37.568 --> 04:39.450
YOU DON'T WANT TO BE
THE GUY WHO PROSECUTES

04:39.450 --> 04:42.663
A WAR HERO
WITH NEUROLOGICAL PROBLEMS.

04:42.663 --> 04:43.994
COME ON, DONNIE.

04:43.994 --> 04:45.906
DO THE RIGHT THING.

04:48.118 --> 04:50.120
Donnie: WHILE BRAVELY
SERVING HER COUNTRY

04:50.120 --> 04:52.002
AS PART OF
OPERATION ENDURING FREEDOM,

04:52.002 --> 04:55.125
SPECIALIST MURPHY DEVELOPED
A NEUROLOGICAL DISORDER

04:55.125 --> 04:56.417
THAT HER DOCTORS BELIEVE

04:56.417 --> 04:57.968
TRIGGERED
HER RECENT ERRATIC BEHAVIOR,

04:57.968 --> 04:59.510
SO AT THIS TIME,

04:59.510 --> 05:02.553
THE U.S. ATTORNEY'S OFFICE
IS DEFERRING PROSECUTION

05:02.553 --> 05:04.685
SO SHE CAN RECEIVE TREATMENT
AT THE V.A. HOSPITAL.

05:04.685 --> 05:06.347
I WOULD URGE EVERYONE

05:06.347 --> 05:10.100
TO GIVE SPECIALIST MURPHY
AND HER HUSBAND THEIR PRIVACY.

05:10.100 --> 05:13.934
IT'S THE LEAST WE CAN DO
FOR A GENUINE AMERICAN HERO.

05:13.934 --> 05:15.606
THANK YOU.
[ CROWD MURMURS ]

05:17.358 --> 05:18.859
GOT TO ADMIT,

05:18.859 --> 05:22.202
I THINK I MIGHT BE
A LITTLE BIT PROUD OF YOU.

05:22.202 --> 05:23.614
YOU WANT TO GRAB A BITE?

05:23.614 --> 05:26.447
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
OH, UM...RAIN CHECK?

05:26.447 --> 05:28.118
SURE.

05:32.713 --> 05:35.125
Miranda: D.J.?

05:37.047 --> 05:39.259
MIRANDA? WHAT --

05:39.259 --> 05:41.131
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

05:41.131 --> 05:42.843
[ Chuckling ]
NICE TO SEE YOU, TOO.

05:42.843 --> 05:45.426
I'M SORRY, I-I DIDN'T MEAN
TO PUT IT THAT WAY.

05:45.426 --> 05:47.057
I'M TEACHING A FEW
MASTER CLASSES.

05:47.057 --> 05:48.679
I'M GONNA BE HERE
FOR A FEW WEEKS.

05:48.679 --> 05:50.270
HUH.

05:50.270 --> 05:52.853
UH, YOUR --
YOUR LAST ALBUM WAS --

05:52.853 --> 05:54.775
WAS WONDERFUL, BY THE WAY.

05:54.775 --> 05:55.816
YOU BOUGHT IT?

05:55.816 --> 05:58.108
MY T.A. MADE ME A TAPE.

05:58.108 --> 06:00.611
STILL ROCKING THE WALKMAN,
I SEE.

06:00.611 --> 06:03.444
YOU KNOW, I HAVE A FEW
DATES COMING UP WITH
THE CHICAGO SYMPHONY.

06:03.444 --> 06:05.616
I'D BE HAPPY
TO COMP YOU A FEW TICKETS.

06:05.616 --> 06:07.327
I'M NOT GREAT WITH CROWDS.

06:07.327 --> 06:08.659
OH.

06:08.659 --> 06:10.370
UH, WELL,
ARE YOU BUSY NOW?

06:10.370 --> 06:12.202
I'D LOVE TO BUY YOU
A CUP OF COFFEE.

06:12.202 --> 06:14.334
I CAN'T DO CAFFEINE.

06:14.334 --> 06:17.377
YOU USED TO LIVE ON
BLACK COFFEE AND JOLT COLA.

06:17.377 --> 06:19.840
I'M SORRY, I'M JUST --
I'M JUST REALLY --

06:19.840 --> 06:23.594
I'M REALLY BUSY
AT THE MOMENT.

06:23.594 --> 06:25.806
OKAY.

06:25.806 --> 06:27.848
WELL,
IT WAS NICE TO SEE YOU.

06:35.726 --> 06:38.729
[ SIMPLE MINDS' "DON'T YOU
(FORGET ABOUT ME)" PLAYS ]

06:38.729 --> 06:41.021
Young Daniel: MIRANDA.

06:41.021 --> 06:43.524
D.J.
HEY.

06:43.524 --> 06:49.700
♪ OOH, OOH, WHOA ♪

06:53.083 --> 06:54.204
WHAT'S WRONG?

06:55.796 --> 06:58.879
UM...

06:58.879 --> 07:00.300
I GOT THIS TODAY.

07:00.300 --> 07:02.713
♪ ...DANCING,
YOU KNOW IT, BABY ♪

07:02.713 --> 07:05.676
UNIVERSITY OF
MUSIC AND PERFORMING ARTS.

07:05.676 --> 07:07.427
VIENNA.

07:07.427 --> 07:11.101
I AUDITIONED LAST YEAR BEFORE
WE STARTED GOING OUT, SO...

07:11.101 --> 07:13.393
IT'S LIKE A...

07:13.393 --> 07:15.055
SUMMER PROGRAM?
NO.

07:15.055 --> 07:17.978
I'D BE TRANSFERRING THERE
IN THE FALL.

07:20.901 --> 07:23.524
[ CHUCKLES ]
SO, ARE YOU GONNA GO?

07:23.524 --> 07:25.235
I DON'T KNOW YET.

07:25.235 --> 07:26.737
I WAS GONNA
GO HOME THIS WEEKEND

07:26.737 --> 07:28.529
TO SEE WHAT
MY PARENTS HAVE TO SAY, BUT...

07:28.529 --> 07:31.411
♪ DON'T YOU ♪
...WHAT DO YOU THINK?

07:31.411 --> 07:34.835
♪ FORGET ABOUT ME ♪

07:34.835 --> 07:37.578
♪ DON'T, DON'T, DON'T, DON'T ♪

07:37.578 --> 07:39.790
♪ DON'T YOU ♪

07:39.790 --> 07:43.423
♪ FORGET ABOUT ME ♪

07:43.423 --> 07:46.176
♪ DON'T, DON'T, DON'T, DON'T ♪

07:46.176 --> 07:47.718
♪ DON'T YOU ♪

07:47.718 --> 07:48.849
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

07:48.849 --> 07:49.970
HEY.

07:49.970 --> 07:51.932
YOU REDEEMING
THAT RAIN CHECK?

07:51.932 --> 07:54.515
REMEMBER LAST WEEK

07:54.515 --> 07:56.476
WHEN I WAS, UH...

07:56.476 --> 07:58.939
PROUD OF YOU
FOR DOING THE RIGHT THING?

07:58.939 --> 08:01.061
YEAH.

08:01.061 --> 08:05.025
TURNS OUT IT MAY NOT HAVE BEEN
THE RIGHT THING AFTER ALL.

08:06.657 --> 08:08.609
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

08:08.609 --> 08:10.571
I FOUND HER
WITH THE BODY,

08:10.571 --> 08:12.452
BLOOD
ALL OVER HER HANDS.

08:17.788 --> 08:20.621
221st.
THAT'S KENDRA'S UNIT.

08:20.621 --> 08:23.173
THEY MUST HAVE
SERVED TOGETHER.

08:23.173 --> 08:24.675
TERRIFIC.

08:24.675 --> 08:27.387
I CUT HER LOOSE,
AND SHE KILLS AN OLD ARMY BUDDY.

08:27.387 --> 08:29.550
GUESS THEY WEREN'T
BUDDIES.

08:43.984 --> 08:45.235
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

08:45.235 --> 08:47.738
THANKS FOR THE HEADS UP
ON MIRANDA.

08:47.738 --> 08:49.199
[ CHUCKLES ]
MIRANDA WHO?

08:50.450 --> 08:51.912
YOU MEAN
YOUR OLD COLLEGE SWEETHEART?

08:51.912 --> 08:53.654
THE ONE THAT GOT AWAY?
THAT MIRANDA?

08:53.654 --> 08:56.076
YOU COULD HAVE WARNED
ME SHE WAS HERE TO
TEACH SOME CLASSES.

08:56.076 --> 08:58.118
I'M NOT THE DEAN
OF THE MUSIC SCHOOL.

08:58.118 --> 09:00.921
HOW THE HELL
WAS I SUPPOSED TO KNOW?

09:00.921 --> 09:03.083
SO, HOW IS SHE, ANYWAY?

09:03.083 --> 09:04.504
I DON'T KNOW.
FINE, I GUESS.

09:04.504 --> 09:06.256
I SPOKE TO HER
FOR ALL OF 30 SECONDS.

09:06.256 --> 09:08.008
I MEAN HOW DOES SHE LOOK?

09:08.008 --> 09:09.379
GORGEOUS.

09:09.379 --> 09:11.471
YOU GONNA GO FOR IT?
YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

09:11.471 --> 09:12.883
I HAVEN'T SEEN HER

09:12.883 --> 09:14.635
SINCE THE DAY OF
OUR VERY UNPLEASANT BREAKUP.

09:14.635 --> 09:16.476
I'M SURE SHE WOULDN'T BE
THE SLIGHTEST BIT INTERESTED.

09:16.476 --> 09:18.138
DANIEL, THAT WAS
A MILLION YEARS AGO.

09:18.138 --> 09:19.810
I'M SURE
SHE'S OVER IT BY NOW.

09:19.810 --> 09:21.481
I DON'T KNOW.

09:21.481 --> 09:23.353
LOOK, IF THIS IS ABOUT
YOUR DIAGNOSIS,

09:23.353 --> 09:24.775
MAYBE SHE ALREADY KNOWS.

09:24.775 --> 09:27.567
IT'S NOT EXACTLY
A STATE SECRET ANYMORE.

09:29.740 --> 09:30.821
HEY, DOC?

09:30.821 --> 09:32.152
UH, KATE JUST CALLED.

09:32.152 --> 09:33.824
SHE SAYS
THEY'RE READY FOR YOU DOWNTOWN.

09:35.826 --> 09:38.158
DEAN HALEY?

09:38.158 --> 09:40.791
[ ZIPPER ZIPS ]

09:40.791 --> 09:42.372
MY CLIENT IS INNOCENT.

09:42.372 --> 09:44.665
SHE WAS FOUND STANDING
OVER LARRY McPHEE'S BODY

09:44.665 --> 09:46.046
WITH BLOOD ON HER HANDS.

09:46.046 --> 09:48.298
KENDRA'S BEEN ON HER MEDS
FOR SEVEN DAYS.

09:48.298 --> 09:51.011
ACCORDING TO HER DOCTORS,
HER BEHAVIOR'S STABILIZED.

09:51.011 --> 09:52.172
SHE'S NOT A THREAT
TO ANYONE.

09:52.172 --> 09:54.014
MR. GENNARO,
I'M FEELING BETTER.

09:54.014 --> 09:55.886
I CAN SPEAK FOR MYSELF.

09:55.886 --> 09:57.848
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED
LAST NIGHT.

09:57.848 --> 10:01.561
I WAS IN MY -- MY HOSPITAL ROOM
WHEN LARRY CALLED.

10:01.561 --> 10:04.314
AND HE TOLD ME
HE WAS IN THE PARKING LOT.

10:04.314 --> 10:06.186
HE SAID HE COULDN'T
COME UP AND SEE ME

10:06.186 --> 10:07.858
BECAUSE VISITING HOURS
WERE OVER.

10:07.858 --> 10:10.070
BUT HE SAID
HE NEEDED TO TALK.

10:10.070 --> 10:11.692
ABOUT WHAT?

10:11.692 --> 10:14.194
HE WOULDN'T SAY
ON THE PHONE,

10:14.194 --> 10:17.868
BUT HE SAID
IT WAS REALLY IMPORTANT, SO --

10:17.868 --> 10:21.081
SO I WENT DOWN
TO MEET HIM, AND --

10:21.081 --> 10:22.873
AND I FOUND HIM LIKE THAT.

10:22.873 --> 10:25.335
AND THERE WAS SO MUCH BLOOD,
YOU KNOW, I TRIED TO STOP IT.

10:25.335 --> 10:28.588
Colonel: I SAW THIS KIND
OF THING AFTER DUNKIRK.

10:28.588 --> 10:30.590
SHELL SHOCK.

10:30.590 --> 10:32.212
BATTLE FATIGUE.

10:32.212 --> 10:33.754
WHAT KIND OF A COUNTRY

10:33.754 --> 10:36.596
SENDS DAMES OUT
TO FIGHT ITS BATTLES, ANYWAY?

10:36.596 --> 10:38.218
NOT THAT THERE'S
ANY POINT IN ENGAGING

10:38.218 --> 10:40.390
IN A CULTURAL DEBATE
WITH ONE OF MY HALLUCINATIONS,

10:40.390 --> 10:42.262
BUT DON'T YOU THINK
A LITTLE RESPECT IS IN ORDER?

10:42.262 --> 10:43.684
SHE'S A DECORATED SOLDIER.

10:43.684 --> 10:46.817
I'M NOT GONNA LISTEN TO
A LECTURE ABOUT RESPECT

10:46.817 --> 10:49.770
FROM SOME PINKO
LIBERAL COLLEGE PROFESSOR.

10:49.770 --> 10:51.191
WE KNOW YOU'VE HAD

10:51.191 --> 10:54.114
SEVERAL SEXUAL PARTNERS
SINCE YOU RETURNED HOME.

10:54.114 --> 10:56.406
WAS LARRY McPHEE
ONE OF THEM?
NO.

10:56.406 --> 10:59.039
I HAVEN'T SEEN LARRY
SINCE AFGHANISTAN.

10:59.039 --> 11:00.620
DID THE TWO OF YOU
HAVE AN AFFAIR

11:00.620 --> 11:02.743
WHILE YOU WERE
SERVING TOGETHER?
NO.

11:02.743 --> 11:04.124
I WOULD NEVER DO THAT.

11:04.124 --> 11:06.286
I'D KEEP MY EYES
ON THIS LITTLE HONEY.

11:07.287 --> 11:09.459
SHE AIN'T GIVING YOU
THE WHOLE PICTURE.

11:11.211 --> 11:12.632
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

11:12.632 --> 11:13.794
DO YOU THINK SHE'S LYING?

11:16.056 --> 11:18.258
Donnie:
WHAT ABOUT THE HUSBAND?

11:18.258 --> 11:20.300
MAYBE HE THOUGHT SHE WAS
SCREWING THE OLD ARMY BUDDY,

11:20.300 --> 11:21.762
SO HE KILLED HIM.

11:21.762 --> 11:23.433
CAN'T BE THE HUSBAND --
HE WAS TENDING BAR

11:23.433 --> 11:25.435
IN FRONT OF 200 PEOPLE
LAST NIGHT.

11:25.435 --> 11:27.107
I WENT TO THE MAT
FOR THIS WOMAN.

11:27.107 --> 11:28.769
DO YOU KNOW
HOW BAD THIS LOOKS?

11:28.769 --> 11:30.941
LISTEN, I DON'T WANT
IT TO BE TRUE ANY
MORE THAN YOU DO,

11:30.941 --> 11:32.362
BUT MAYBE SHE'S GUILTY.

11:32.362 --> 11:33.774
NO, NO, NO.

11:33.774 --> 11:35.195
THE MEDS ARE WORKING.
SHE'S NOT VIOLENT.

11:35.195 --> 11:36.446
MY GUT SAYS
SHE DIDN'T DO THIS.

11:36.446 --> 11:37.738
GREAT.

11:37.738 --> 11:39.369
I SAY WE GO WITH DANIEL'S GUT
ON THIS ONE.

11:39.369 --> 11:41.411
COME ON, GUYS.
DO YOUR THING.

11:41.411 --> 11:43.744
PROVE SHE'S INNOCENT.

11:43.744 --> 11:45.285
[ SIGHS ]

11:45.285 --> 11:47.037
CAN YOU THINK OF ANYONE

11:47.037 --> 11:49.129
WHO MIGHT'VE WANTED TO
HARM YOUR HUSBAND?

11:49.129 --> 11:51.251
I CAN'T THINK OF ANYONE.

11:51.251 --> 11:52.632
WHAT ABOUT KENDRA MURPHY?

11:52.632 --> 11:54.334
DID LARRY
EVER MENTION HER?

11:54.334 --> 11:56.256
I NEVER EVEN HEARD HER NAME
UNTIL LAST WEEK

11:56.256 --> 11:57.597
WHEN SHE BLEW UP
THAT STORE.

11:59.469 --> 12:00.971
LARRY SEEMED PRETTY UPSET
ABOUT IT

12:00.971 --> 12:02.302
WHEN WE SAW IT
IN THE NEWS.

12:02.302 --> 12:03.603
UPSET HOW?

12:03.603 --> 12:06.686
HE JUST SAID THAT
SHE DESERVED BETTER.

12:06.686 --> 12:08.018
I ASKED HIM
WHAT HE MEANT,

12:08.018 --> 12:09.309
BUT HE DIDN'T WANT TO
TALK ABOUT IT.

12:09.309 --> 12:11.812
WHAT TIME DID HE LEAVE
LAST NIGHT?

12:11.812 --> 12:13.944
AROUND 9:30, I THINK.

12:13.944 --> 12:15.315
DID HE SAY
WHERE HE WAS GOING?

12:15.315 --> 12:17.737
NO.
HE JUST TOOK OFF.

12:17.737 --> 12:20.620
HE WAS ON THE PHONE
A FEW MINUTES EARLIER.

12:20.620 --> 12:22.622
HE WAS IN THE GARAGE
AND THE DOOR WAS CLOSED,

12:22.622 --> 12:24.785
SO I COULDN'T MAKE OUT
MOST OF WHAT HE WAS SAYING,

12:24.785 --> 12:26.746
BUT HE WAS ARGUING.

12:27.958 --> 12:31.711
I HEARD HIM SAY,
"WE GOT TO MAKE THIS RIGHT."

12:31.711 --> 12:34.174
AND THEN HE HUNG UP
AND LEFT.

12:34.174 --> 12:36.636
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHO HE WAS TALKING TO?

12:38.678 --> 12:41.011
Kate: MR. HICKS, WHAT DID
LARRY MEAN WHEN HE SAID,

12:41.011 --> 12:42.762
"WE GOT TO
MAKE THIS RIGHT"?

12:42.762 --> 12:45.185
REALLY DON'T REMEMBER.

12:45.185 --> 12:46.766
ANTHONY, I KNOW

12:46.766 --> 12:48.849
BEING IN THIS ROOM
COULD BE UNNERVING,

12:48.849 --> 12:50.600
BUT THAT'S NOT WHY
YOU'RE SWEATING

12:50.600 --> 12:52.062
AND YOUR HANDS
ARE SHAKING.

12:52.062 --> 12:54.154
HOW LONG HAS IT BEEN?

12:54.154 --> 12:55.155
EXCUSE ME?

12:55.155 --> 12:56.526
SINCE YOUR LAST FIX.

12:56.526 --> 12:58.358
YOU CAME BACK
FROM AFGHANISTAN

12:58.358 --> 13:00.320
AND DEVELOPED A HABIT,
DIDN'T YOU?

13:00.320 --> 13:02.202
HEROIN POSSESSION?

13:02.202 --> 13:04.034
YEAH, SO?

13:04.034 --> 13:07.327
YOU KNOW, A LOT OF VETS
HAVE TROUBLE ADJUSTING.

13:07.327 --> 13:10.580
LISTEN, I CAN
TALK TO THE PROSECUTOR,

13:10.580 --> 13:12.082
SEE WHAT HE CAN DO ABOUT

13:12.082 --> 13:14.044
GETTING THIS POSSESSION CHARGE
THROWN OUT,

13:14.044 --> 13:15.966
BUT FIRST,

13:15.966 --> 13:18.048
YOU GOT TO TELL ME
WHAT YOU AND LARRY
WERE TALKING ABOUT.

13:18.048 --> 13:20.550
[ SNIFFLES ]

13:20.550 --> 13:22.382
I WANT TO TALK TO A LAWYER.

13:25.055 --> 13:26.977
YOU COMMANDED BRAVO COMPANY
OF THE 221st?

13:26.977 --> 13:28.228
YES, MA'AM.

13:28.228 --> 13:29.809
ONE MINUTE
YOU'RE A WEEKEND WARRIOR,

13:29.809 --> 13:31.101
THE NEXT THING YOU KNOW,

13:31.101 --> 13:32.522
YOU'RE DODGING BULLETS
IN A KILL ZONE.

13:32.522 --> 13:35.065
SO, YOU WERE A COMBAT UNIT?
NOT EXACTLY.

13:35.065 --> 13:36.897
WE WERE ASSIGNED TO
OPERATION THRASHER.

13:36.897 --> 13:39.399
WHAT IS THAT?
SOME COVERT TORTURE PROGRAM?

13:39.399 --> 13:41.571
IT'S NOT AS TOUGH
AS IT SOUNDS.

13:41.571 --> 13:44.444
WE TRAINED THE LOCALS
IN FARMING AND IRRIGATION --

13:44.444 --> 13:45.996
HEARTS AND MINDS
KIND OF THING.

13:45.996 --> 13:49.659
NOW, ANTHONY HICKS
WAS UNDER YOUR COMMAND, AS WELL.

13:49.659 --> 13:51.541
ISN'T THAT RIGHT?
YES, MA'AM.

13:51.541 --> 13:54.414
WAS HE INVOLVED IN
ANY DISORDERLY CONDUCT?

13:54.414 --> 13:56.336
I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE GETTING AT.

13:56.336 --> 13:59.089
HICKS HAS A MONKEY ON HIS BACK
WITH THIS DRUG STUFF,

13:59.089 --> 14:02.262
BUT I DON'T THINK
HE COULD KILL ANYBODY.

14:02.262 --> 14:05.635
THIS WHOLE THING'S
JUST IRONIC AS HELL.

14:05.635 --> 14:06.967
HOW DO YOU MEAN?

14:06.967 --> 14:08.348
[ SIGHS ]

14:08.348 --> 14:10.430
KENDRA RISKED HER LIFE
TO SAVE THOSE TWO GUYS.

14:10.430 --> 14:12.432
THAT'S WHY I PUT HER UP
FOR THE SILVER STAR.

14:12.432 --> 14:13.733
WAIT. WAIT A MINUTE.

14:13.733 --> 14:15.685
THE VICTIM
AND THE DRUG ADDICT --

14:15.685 --> 14:17.277
THOSE WERE
THE TWO GUYS SHE SAVED?

14:17.277 --> 14:18.438
THAT'S RIGHT.

14:19.940 --> 14:21.942
CAN YOU TELL US
WHAT HAPPENED?

14:21.942 --> 14:25.115
A CONVOY
HAD JUST LEFT QALAT VALLEY

14:25.115 --> 14:27.617
WHEN WE WERE AMBUSHED.

14:34.794 --> 14:36.456
THE TALIBAN SET OFF
AN I.E.D.

14:36.456 --> 14:37.877
WHAT THE HELL?!

14:37.877 --> 14:39.589
IT BLEW THE AXLE OFF
THE HUMVEE OUT IN THE FRONT.

14:39.589 --> 14:41.131
WE WERE FISH IN A BARREL.

14:41.131 --> 14:43.423
I GOT ON THE HORN,
ORDERED McPHEE AND HICKS

14:43.423 --> 14:44.965
TO GET OUT THERE
AND RETURN FIRE.

15:00.320 --> 15:03.613
BUT THE BAD GUYS WERE
BETTER ARMED THAN WE REALIZED.

15:13.123 --> 15:16.586
THREE MEN
WERE IN THAT VEHICLE.

15:16.586 --> 15:19.039
KENDRA
DIDN'T WAIT FOR ORDERS.

15:19.039 --> 15:20.920
SHE RAN STRAIGHT FOR
McPHEE AND HICKS.

15:34.014 --> 15:37.057
[ GUN COCKS ]

15:49.829 --> 15:52.372
SHE BLEW
THOSE SONS OF BITCHES AWAY.

15:52.372 --> 15:54.074
KENDRA'S SERVICE RECORD

15:54.074 --> 15:56.376
SAYS THAT SHE WAS TRANSFERRED
TO ANOTHER UNIT.

15:56.376 --> 15:58.578
YEAH. A WEEK OR SO
AFTER THAT BATTLE.

15:58.578 --> 16:00.250
WHY WOULD YOU
PUT HER UP FOR A SILVER STAR

16:00.250 --> 16:01.541
AND THEN
HAVE HER TRANSFERRED?

16:01.541 --> 16:03.543
SHE ASKED FOR THE TRANSFER.

16:03.543 --> 16:05.385
WHY?

16:05.385 --> 16:08.088
SHE MADE AN ALLEGATION
AGAINST ANOTHER SOLDIER.

16:08.088 --> 16:10.350
WHAT KIND OF
AN ALLEGATION?

16:10.350 --> 16:12.682
UH...

16:12.682 --> 16:14.264
SHE CLAIMED
SHE'D BEEN RAPED.

16:16.436 --> 16:18.728
DID SHE TELL YOU
WHO DID IT?

16:18.728 --> 16:20.400
I DON'T WANT TO SULLY

16:20.400 --> 16:22.402
THE REPUTATION
OF A FELLOW SOLDIER

16:22.402 --> 16:24.524
OVER AN
UNSUBSTANTIATED ALLEGATION.

16:24.524 --> 16:27.907
IF YOU WANT TO SUBPOENA ME,
I'LL ANSWER ANY QUESTIONS,

16:27.907 --> 16:31.111
BUT SHORT OF THAT,
I SUGGEST YOU TALK TO KENDRA.

16:38.918 --> 16:41.041
I DON'T THINK
I'M SUPPOSED TO TALK TO YOU

16:41.041 --> 16:42.172
WITHOUT MY ATTORNEY HERE.

16:42.172 --> 16:43.793
LISTEN,
I WANT TO BELIEVE

16:43.793 --> 16:45.885
THAT YOU DIDN'T KILL
LARRY McPHEE,

16:45.885 --> 16:48.128
BUT IF HE RAPED YOU
AND YOU DON'T TELL ME,

16:48.128 --> 16:49.969
IT MAKES YOU LOOK
MORE GUILTY.

16:49.969 --> 16:53.473
IT WASN'T LARRY,
BUT HE KNEW ABOUT IT.

16:53.473 --> 16:55.305
WHO WAS IT?

16:55.305 --> 16:57.477
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

16:57.477 --> 16:59.139
SERGEANT RICKFORD,

16:59.139 --> 17:02.102
OUR SQUAD LEADER.

17:02.102 --> 17:04.234
HE HAD IT OUT FOR ME
EVER SINCE THE AMBUSH.

17:04.234 --> 17:05.525
WHY?

17:05.525 --> 17:07.817
BECAUSE OF
SOMETHING THAT HAPPENED

17:07.817 --> 17:09.739
DURING THE FIREFIGHT.

17:09.739 --> 17:12.782
WE WERE PINNED DOWN,
TAKING FIRE.

17:22.662 --> 17:24.834
OUR GUNNER WAS TAKEN OUT.

17:28.007 --> 17:29.339
I THINK HE'S DEAD, SIR!

17:29.339 --> 17:31.091
RICKFORD,
TAKE OVER THE 240.

17:32.632 --> 17:33.843
SERGEANT, GET UP THERE!

17:33.843 --> 17:36.436
Kendra:
RICKFORD JUST FROZE...

17:36.436 --> 17:38.017
I GOT IT, SIR.

17:40.310 --> 17:41.391
...SO I
TOOK OVER THE TURRET.

17:48.108 --> 17:52.031
A COUPLE DAYS LATER,
BACK AT BASE,

17:52.031 --> 17:54.073
RICKFORD CAME TO SEE ME.

17:54.073 --> 17:56.656
McPHEE AND HICKS
WERE WITH HIM.

17:59.539 --> 18:01.161
I HEARD YOU'VE BEEN
TALKING ABOUT ME.

18:01.161 --> 18:02.702
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, SARGE?

18:02.702 --> 18:06.005
WORD AROUND BASE IS THAT
I'M A CANDY-ASS BITCH

18:06.005 --> 18:08.378
WHO DISOBEYED A DIRECT ORDER
IN THE MIDDLE OF AN ENGAGEMENT.

18:08.378 --> 18:10.049
I DIDN'T
TELL ANYBODY THAT.

18:12.342 --> 18:14.384
YOU THINK TO BE
SOME KIND OF HERO,

18:14.384 --> 18:16.556
YOU GOT TO LIE AND
MAKE EVERYBODY ELSE LOOK BAD?

18:18.888 --> 18:20.019
GET OUT OF MY FACE.

18:20.019 --> 18:21.311
TAKE A WALK, GUYS.

18:21.311 --> 18:23.022
THIS IS BETWEEN ME
AND THIS LYING SLUT.

18:24.224 --> 18:25.935
JUST CHILL OUT, OKAY?
I SAID TAKE A WALK!

18:27.317 --> 18:28.858
COME ON.

18:30.280 --> 18:31.781
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

18:31.781 --> 18:33.363
YOU'RE NOT GOING
ANYWHERE.

18:38.037 --> 18:40.370
YOU'RE NOT SO BRAVE NOW.

18:40.370 --> 18:41.331
ARE YOU, BITCH?

18:43.583 --> 18:47.126
THOSE THREE ASSHOLES --
THEY STUCK TOGETHER.

18:47.126 --> 18:49.048
THEY DENIED
THE WHOLE THING.

18:49.048 --> 18:52.802
THE C.O. SAID
IT WAS THEIR WORD AGAINST MINE.

18:52.802 --> 18:54.133
SO, THAT WAS IT?

18:54.133 --> 18:55.885
THE C.O. DID OFFER
TO SEND THE REPORT

18:55.885 --> 18:57.217
UP THE CHAIN OF COMMAND,

18:57.217 --> 18:59.929
BUT I KNEW
HOW THAT WAS GONNA GO.

18:59.929 --> 19:03.763
I'M VERY, VERY SORRY THAT
THAT HAPPENED TO YOU, KENDRA.

19:03.763 --> 19:05.725
THIS HAPPENS
TO A LOT OF WOMEN.

19:05.725 --> 19:09.529
ALMOST NOBODY
GETS PUNISHED.

19:09.529 --> 19:12.772
THEY CALL ME
A LIAR OR A SLUT,

19:12.772 --> 19:15.325
SO I WANTED TO PUT THIS
BEHIND ME.

19:15.325 --> 19:17.076
SO I ASKED FOR A TRANSFER.

19:17.076 --> 19:21.831
SO, WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME MORE
ABOUT THIS SERGEANT RICKFORD?

19:21.831 --> 19:24.374
[ SCOFFS SOFTLY ]

19:24.374 --> 19:27.086
YOU'D THINK HE WALKED
ON WATER THE WAY THE
BRASS HANDLED HIM.

19:27.086 --> 19:29.289
HE GOT SPECIAL TREATMENT?

19:29.289 --> 19:31.961
HIS DAD'S A CONGRESSMAN.

19:31.961 --> 19:35.385
WAIT,
YOU MEAN EVAN RICKFORD,

19:35.385 --> 19:37.637
THE CHAIRMAN OF THE HOUSE
ARMED SERVICES COMMITTEE --

19:37.637 --> 19:39.719
HIS SON
IS THE ONE WHO RAPED YOU?

19:44.103 --> 19:45.355
MEET THE BLACK SHEEP

19:45.355 --> 19:47.106
OF THE DISTINGUISHED
RICKFORD FAMILY.

19:47.106 --> 19:48.648
KICKED OUT OF
BOARDING SCHOOL,

19:48.648 --> 19:51.361
MULTIPLE DUIs,
THREE STINTS IN REHAB,

19:51.361 --> 19:53.313
BUT IT LOOKS LIKE
BLAKE RICKFORD

19:53.313 --> 19:54.654
HAD FINALLY
CLEANED UP HIS ACT

19:54.654 --> 19:57.026
WHEN HE JOINED
THE NATIONAL GUARD.

19:57.026 --> 19:58.698
SERVED HIS COUNTRY,
CAME HOME,

19:58.698 --> 20:00.820
LANDED A BIG JOB
AT A TOP FINANCIAL FIRM.

20:00.820 --> 20:02.582
I HAVE ZERO PROBLEM
BELIEVING

20:02.582 --> 20:05.204
THIS OVER-PRIVILEGED FRAT BOY
SEXUALLY ASSAULTED KENDRA,

20:05.204 --> 20:07.166
BUT WHAT'S THE CONNECTION
TO LARRY McPHEE'S MURDER?

20:07.166 --> 20:08.328
TRY THIS ON.

20:08.328 --> 20:10.169
WE KNOW FROM LARRY'S WIFE

20:10.169 --> 20:12.672
THAT LARRY TOOK THE NEWS
OF KENDRA'S ARREST PRETTY HARD.

20:12.672 --> 20:16.466
MAYBE HE FELT GUILTY ABOUT
LYING TO COVER UP THE RAPE.

20:16.466 --> 20:19.509
SO LARRY CALLS UP HICKS,
TELLS HIM HE'S GONNA COME CLEAN.

20:19.509 --> 20:21.220
UH, WHAT DID HE SAY?
"WE GOT TO MAKE THIS RIGHT."

20:21.220 --> 20:22.552
HICKS TRIES TO
TALK LARRY OUT OF IT,

20:22.552 --> 20:24.053
BUT LARRY WON'T LISTEN.

20:24.053 --> 20:26.516
NOW HICKS IS WORRIED THAT
IF LARRY CHANGES HIS STORY

20:26.516 --> 20:28.227
THAT HE'S GONNA BE
HUNG OUT TO DRY,

20:28.227 --> 20:29.769
SO HICKS CALLS UP THE RAPIST

20:29.769 --> 20:32.692
AND TELLS HIM THAT LARRY'S
ON HIS WAY TO THE HOSPITAL

20:32.692 --> 20:34.854
TO TELL KENDRA THAT
HE'S READY TO TELL THE TRUTH.

20:34.854 --> 20:36.276
RICKFORD
RUSHES OVER THERE,

20:36.276 --> 20:37.987
KILLS LARRY
BEFORE HE CAN SAY ANYTHING.

20:38.818 --> 20:40.199
HOW DO WE PROVE IT?

20:40.199 --> 20:42.782
I COULD ASK THE RAPIST.

20:50.129 --> 20:52.502
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

20:52.502 --> 20:54.464
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

20:58.718 --> 21:00.590
NICE WHEELS.

21:00.590 --> 21:02.051
HOW ABOUT
I TAKE YOU FOR A RIDE?

21:02.051 --> 21:03.262
NO, THAT'S OKAY.

21:03.262 --> 21:05.054
I GOT MY OWN CAR --
GOVERNMENT ISSUED.

21:05.054 --> 21:06.936
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI,
FBI.

21:06.936 --> 21:08.438
I'M HERE ABOUT
LARRY McPHEE.

21:08.438 --> 21:11.481
I COULDN'T BELIEVE IT
WHEN I HEARD.

21:11.481 --> 21:13.022
LARRY WAS
LIKE A BROTHER TO ME.

21:13.022 --> 21:15.895
WHERE WERE YOU TWO NIGHTS AGO
WHEN HE WAS KILLED?

21:15.895 --> 21:18.157
[ CHUCKLES ]
ARE YOU ACTUALLY ACCUSING ME?

21:19.238 --> 21:21.361
WHY THE HELL WOULD I KILL
ONE OF MY BEST FRIENDS?

21:21.361 --> 21:23.242
BECAUSE HE KNEW THAT
YOU RAPED KENDRA MURPHY.

21:23.242 --> 21:24.664
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

21:24.664 --> 21:27.076
FIRST OF ALL,
THAT CRAZY BITCH CAME ON TO ME.

21:27.076 --> 21:28.748
THE SECOND I TURN HER DOWN,

21:28.748 --> 21:32.251
SHE RUNS OFF TO THE C.O.
WITH SOME BULLSHIT ALLEGATIONS.

21:32.251 --> 21:33.463
EVERYONE IN THE UNIT
KNEW THAT GIRL WAS NUTS.

21:33.463 --> 21:35.044
SO, YOU DENY RAPING HER?

21:35.044 --> 21:38.007
RAPE HER?
WE NEVER EVEN HAD SEX.

21:39.258 --> 21:41.421
SHE'S A LITTLE TOO BUTCH
FOR MY TASTE.

21:41.421 --> 21:43.763
SO, WHERE WERE YOU
TWO NIGHTS AGO?

21:43.763 --> 21:47.266
ON MY FATHER'S BOAT
ON LAKE MICHIGAN.

21:47.266 --> 21:50.600
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME,
YOU CAN ASK HIM YOURSELF.

21:57.567 --> 22:00.109
TELL CARL I NEED
FIVE MINUTES, OKAY?

22:00.109 --> 22:01.821
GET ME SOME LUNCH.

22:03.443 --> 22:04.784
CONGRESSMAN,
THANK YOU FOR SEEING ME

22:04.784 --> 22:06.035
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

22:06.035 --> 22:07.497
NO TROUBLE AT ALL,
AGENT MORETTI.

22:07.497 --> 22:11.210
I WAS JUST HOPING TO CONFIRM
SOME INFORMATION.

22:11.210 --> 22:13.913
MAYBE I CAN SAVE US BOTH
A LITTLE TIME HERE.

22:13.913 --> 22:16.956
BLAKE WAS WITH ME
ON MY YACHT

22:16.956 --> 22:20.089
THE NIGHT THAT THIS, UH,
McPHEE FELLA WAS KILLED.

22:20.089 --> 22:23.763
SO, JUST TO BE CLEAR,
HE TOLD YOU WHAT HE TOLD ME.

22:23.763 --> 22:25.344
WELL,
HE TELLS ME EVERYTHING,

22:25.344 --> 22:26.806
BECAUSE SOONER OR LATER,
I'M GONNA LEARN ABOUT IT ANYWAY.

22:26.806 --> 22:30.600
MY SON MAY HAVE MADE
SOME BAD CHOICES IN THE PAST,

22:30.600 --> 22:32.932
BUT HE'S NOT A MURDERER
OR A RAPIST.

22:32.932 --> 22:34.974
AND BLAKE HAS WORKED
LONG AND HARD

22:34.974 --> 22:36.606
TO AMEND
HIS YOUTHFUL INDISCRETIONS.

22:36.606 --> 22:38.648
THAT'S WHY HE WENT OFF
TO FIGHT FOR HIS COUNTRY.

22:38.648 --> 22:40.650
I APPRECIATE HIS SERVICE.

22:40.650 --> 22:44.824
AS I DO YOURS,
AGENT MORETTI.

22:44.824 --> 22:46.075
THANK YOU
FOR YOUR TIME, SIR.

22:49.328 --> 22:51.491
OH, AND
A WORD OF ADVICE.

22:51.491 --> 22:53.623
OVERREACHING --

22:53.623 --> 22:55.955
THAT CAN BE HAZARDOUS
TO ONE'S CAREER.

23:06.265 --> 23:08.558
[ BACH'S CELLO SUITE NO. FIVE
PLAYS ]

23:28.197 --> 23:29.699
I DON'T THINK
I'VE EVER HEARD THAT SUITE

23:29.699 --> 23:31.030
PLAYED MORE BEAUTIFULLY.

23:31.030 --> 23:32.201
THANK YOU.

23:32.201 --> 23:35.334
I WAS AN IDIOT
THE OTHER DAY.

23:35.334 --> 23:36.996
I'M SORRY.

23:36.996 --> 23:38.708
FORGET ABOUT IT.

23:38.708 --> 23:42.381
I WAS WONDERING IF I COULD
BUY YOU THAT CUP OF COFFEE.

23:44.383 --> 23:46.215
I AM KIND OF HUNGRY.

23:46.215 --> 23:48.097
DO YOU REMEMBER
THAT REALLY FANCY

23:48.097 --> 23:50.680
FIVE-STAR RESTAURANT
IN LINCOLN PARK?

23:50.680 --> 23:52.932
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:52.932 --> 23:56.055
IT'S BEEN A WHILE SINCE
I'VE HAD A REAL CHICAGO DOG.

23:56.055 --> 23:57.897
I KNOW. ME TOO.

23:57.897 --> 23:59.859
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:02.021 --> 24:03.442
Natalie: DANIEL,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

24:03.442 --> 24:06.275
YOU'RE NOT 21 ANYMORE,
YOU KNOW.

24:06.275 --> 24:07.487
HAVE YOU EVEN
THOUGHT ABOUT

24:07.487 --> 24:08.948
WHAT THE MYSTERY MEAT
IN THAT THING

24:08.948 --> 24:10.990
WILL DO
TO YOUR DIGESTIVE TRACT?

24:13.242 --> 24:14.744
AND WHAT ABOUT THE BUN?

24:14.744 --> 24:16.455
YOU KNOW THAT GLUTEN

24:16.455 --> 24:18.207
IS A PATHOGENIC FACTOR
IN SCHIZOPHRENIA.

24:22.041 --> 24:23.422
IS THERE
SOMETHING WRONG?

24:23.422 --> 24:24.253
NO.

24:24.253 --> 24:26.045
NO, I'M, UM...

24:26.045 --> 24:28.007
NOT THAT HUNGRY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:28.007 --> 24:30.469
BUT YOU, PLEASE, PLEASE.
DIVE IN.

24:30.469 --> 24:31.180
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:35.434 --> 24:36.726
MMM.

24:40.600 --> 24:41.861
YOU WENT TO HIS OFFICE?

24:42.902 --> 24:44.063
WHAT THE HELL
WERE YOU THINKING?

24:44.063 --> 24:45.775
I WAS CONFIRMING AN ALIBI.

24:45.775 --> 24:48.107
NOW I JUST NEED SUBPOENAS
FOR BLAKE RICKFORD'S

24:48.107 --> 24:50.369
CELL, CAR GPS, E-MAIL --

24:50.369 --> 24:51.571
