BUT HE'S JUST COVERING

24:56.455 --> 24:58.618
FOR HIS LYING, RAPING,
MURDERING SON.

24:58.618 --> 25:00.289
GET ME THOSE RECORDS.
I'LL PROVE IT.

25:00.289 --> 25:02.251
