KENDRA DID IT,

25:03.793 --> 25:05.835
AND I'VE GOT THE BOSSES
BREATHING DOWN MY NECK

25:05.835 --> 25:07.466
TO CLOSE THIS THING.
OKAY, FINE.

25:07.466 --> 25:09.629
YOU WON'T GET ME WHAT I NEED,
I'LL FIND SOMEONE WHO WILL.

25:09.629 --> 25:10.930
YOU'RE DOING IT AGAIN,
KATE.

25:10.930 --> 25:12.181
DOING WHAT?

25:12.181 --> 25:14.634
WHAT DID THE DEPUTY DIRECTOR
CALL IT?

25:14.634 --> 25:18.638
EXCEEDING THE SCOPE
OF YOUR ASSIGNED INVESTIGATIONS.

25:18.638 --> 25:21.020
IT GOT YOU
BOUNCED OUT OF D.C.

25:21.020 --> 25:23.813
PLEASE, KATE,
I'M BEGGING YOU.

25:23.813 --> 25:25.444
LET THIS ONE GO.

25:25.444 --> 25:29.649
THAT SON OF A BITCH
GOT AWAY WITH RAPING A WAR HERO.

25:29.649 --> 25:31.571
NOW, MAYBE THERE'S
NOTHING I CAN DO ABOUT THAT,

25:31.571 --> 25:33.653
BUT HE SURE AS HELL ISN'T GONNA
GET AWAY WITH MURDER --

25:33.653 --> 25:34.914
NOT ON MY WATCH.

25:36.746 --> 25:38.658
ALL RIGHT.

25:38.658 --> 25:41.040
THEN BRING ME
SOME REAL EVIDENCE --

25:41.040 --> 25:43.332
SOMETHING
THAT I CAN TAKE TO A JUDGE,

25:43.332 --> 25:44.754
AND I'LL SEE
WHAT I CAN DO.

25:46.165 --> 25:47.667
Miranda: I'M WALKING
THROUGH GREENWICH VILLAGE,

25:47.667 --> 25:50.549
AND...
I PASS A BOOKSTORE.

25:50.549 --> 25:52.341
AND THERE IN THE WINDOW

25:52.341 --> 25:55.554
IS A LIFE-SIZE
CARDBOARD CUT-OUT OF YOU.

25:55.554 --> 25:57.266
OH, GOD.

25:57.266 --> 25:59.729
THE FUTURE BEST-SELLER
FROM AUTHOR DANIEL J. PIERCE --

25:59.729 --> 26:01.350
"SPECTRES
OF A HUMAN MIND."

26:01.350 --> 26:02.942
MM-HMM.

26:02.942 --> 26:04.563
I ALWAYS THOUGHT I'D SEE YOU
ON THE COVER OF SOMETHING --

26:04.563 --> 26:06.025
JUST THOUGHT IT WOULD BE
ROLLING STONE.

26:06.025 --> 26:07.647
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH.

26:07.647 --> 26:09.568
