DIFFERENT WAY.

26:09.568 --> 26:11.110
BUT YOU -- LOOK AT YOU.

26:11.110 --> 26:12.742
YOU'RE EXACTLY
WHERE YOU WANTED TO BE.

26:12.742 --> 26:14.864
YOU'RE PLAYING
ALL OVER THE WORLD.

26:14.864 --> 26:16.495
YOU DID IT.

26:16.495 --> 26:19.619
WELL, I WOULDN'T TRADE
THE LAST 20 YEARS FOR ANYTHING,

26:19.619 --> 26:22.121
BUT I HAVE BEEN THINKING
IT MIGHT BE TIME

26:22.121 --> 26:23.753
TO PUT DOWN SOME ROOTS
SOMEWHERE.

26:23.753 --> 26:26.085
ANY PLACE IN PARTICULAR?

26:26.085 --> 26:28.337
NOT YET.

26:28.337 --> 26:30.419
BUT IT IS NICE
TO BE BACK IN CHICAGO.

26:30.419 --> 26:32.091
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:32.091 --> 26:33.673
Young Daniel: SHE'S NEVER COMING
BACK TO CHICAGO. I KNOW IT.

26:33.673 --> 26:35.094
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
SHE WENT TO VISIT HER PARENTS

26:35.094 --> 26:36.425
JUST FOR THE WEEKEND.

26:36.425 --> 26:37.677
I MEAN
SHE'S NOT COMING BACK

26:37.677 --> 26:40.059
IF SHE GOES TO VIENNA,
DUMBASS.

26:40.059 --> 26:42.021
[ SIGHS ]
SHE'S ONLY BEEN GONE 12 HOURS,

26:42.021 --> 26:43.482
AND I'M ALREADY MISERABLE.

26:43.482 --> 26:45.224
I CAN'T SLEEP.
I CAN'T STUDY.

26:45.224 --> 26:46.726
MAYBE SHE'S
TESTING YOU.

26:46.726 --> 26:48.277
MAYBE SHE
MADE UP THIS WHOLE THING

26:48.277 --> 26:50.189
TO FIND OUT IF
YOU REALLY WANT TO BE WITH HER.

26:50.189 --> 26:52.732
GEEZ, PAUL.
PARANOID MUCH?

26:52.732 --> 26:55.074
SHE'D BE CRAZY
NOT TO TAKE THIS.

26:55.074 --> 26:56.575
SHE'S GONNA FORGET ABOUT ME

26:56.575 --> 26:58.407
AND RUN OFF TO THE ALPS
WITH ONE OF THE VON TRAPPS.

26:58.407 --> 27:01.450
DUDE, LOOK.
YOU'RE WAY TOO INTO THIS GIRL.

27:01.450 --> 27:03.002
YOU NEED TO GET HER
OUT OF YOUR HEAD.

27:03.002 --> 27:06.706
JUST...
BLOW OFF SOME STEAM.

27:06.706 --> 27:08.047
Kate:
DANIEL, I NEED YOUR HELP.

27:08.047 --> 27:09.799
I REALLY GOT TO
CATCH THIS...

27:09.799 --> 27:12.922
HI. I DIDN'T REALIZE
THAT YOU HAD COMPANY.

27:12.922 --> 27:14.133
NO, NO, NO.
NO, NO. UH...

27:14.133 --> 27:15.424
MIRANDA STILES,
KATE MORETTI.

27:15.424 --> 27:16.425
NICE TO MEET YOU.

27:16.425 --> 27:17.556
LIKEWISE.

27:17.556 --> 27:19.258
UM, I CAN COME BACK.

27:19.258 --> 27:21.971
I WAS JUST LEAVING.

27:21.971 --> 27:22.812
ARE YOU SURE?

27:22.812 --> 27:24.894
YEAH.

27:24.894 --> 27:26.475
I'LL SEE YOU LATER?

27:26.475 --> 27:28.027
YEP. OKAY.

27:32.071 --> 27:33.072
BYE, D.J.

27:38.157 --> 27:38.948
"D.J."?

27:38.948 --> 27:40.409
DON'T. JUST....

27:40.409 --> 27:42.241
I GOT NOTHING
ON RICKFORD.

27:42.241 --> 27:44.453
WHAT I NEED IS SOME EVIDENCE
TO JUSTIFY A SUBPOENA.

27:44.453 --> 27:45.915
I JUST FEEL LIKE
THERE MUST BE SOMETHING

27:45.915 --> 27:47.997
THAT WE'VE BEEN MISSING.

27:47.997 --> 27:49.839
WHAT ABOUT
THAT ADDICT WE TALKED TO?

27:49.839 --> 27:52.051
ANTHONY HICKS?
NO, HE'S LAWYERED UP, REMEMBER?

27:52.051 --> 27:54.003
HE'S DONE TALKING.
WELL, MAYBE HE'LL TALK

27:54.003 --> 27:56.005
IF WE FIND HIM
IN THE RIGHT STATE OF MIND.

27:56.005 --> 27:57.426
YOU KNOW,
HE IS SELF-MEDICATING

27:57.426 --> 27:58.848
WITH A REAL-LIFE
TRUTH SERUM.

27:58.848 --> 28:00.599
WAIT, SINCE WHEN IS HEROIN
A TRUTH SERUM?

28:00.599 --> 28:03.102
SOME PEOPLE ARE MORE OPEN
AND FORTHCOMING

28:03.102 --> 28:04.764
WHEN THEIR ENDORPHINS
ARE FLOWING.

28:04.764 --> 28:06.225
LET'S SEE IF WE CAN CATCH HIM
WHILE HE'S STILL HIGH.

28:07.646 --> 28:09.809
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

28:14.814 --> 28:16.776
MR. HICKS?

28:18.697 --> 28:21.580
OH, GEEZ.

28:21.580 --> 28:24.163
[ Cellphone dialing ]

28:24.163 --> 28:26.085
IT'S MORETTI.
I NEED AN AMBULANCE.

28:26.085 --> 28:29.959
BETTER MAKE IT
THE CORONER.

28:37.797 --> 28:40.219
LISTEN TO THIS -- ANTHONY HICKS'
FINAL STATUS UPDATE.

28:40.219 --> 28:41.801
"WAR DON'T ENNOBLE MEN.

28:41.801 --> 28:43.472
"IT TURNS THEM INTO DOGS.

28:43.472 --> 28:47.016
"I'M A NO-GOOD JUNKIE LOSER
WHO SMASHED MY FRIEND'S HEAD IN.

28:47.016 --> 28:48.727
I DON'T DESERVE TO LIVE."

28:48.727 --> 28:49.849
IT'S A SUICIDE NOTE.

28:49.849 --> 28:51.400
YEAH,
AND A MURDER CONFESSION

28:51.400 --> 28:53.692
POSTED ONLINE
FOR EVERYONE TO SEE.

28:53.692 --> 28:55.614
IT SEEMS
A LITTLE CONVENIENT.

28:55.614 --> 28:56.986
MAYBE, BUT -- BUT --

28:56.986 --> 28:59.568
BUT IT DOES TRACK WITH
PART OF OUR THEORY.

28:59.568 --> 29:01.700
SO, LARRY WANTS TO COME CLEAN
ABOUT THE RAPE.

29:01.700 --> 29:04.123
HE CALLS HICKS,
WHO TRIES TO TALK HIM OUT OF IT.

29:04.123 --> 29:07.326
LARRY WON'T LISTEN,
SO HICKS DRIVES TO THE V.A.

29:07.326 --> 29:08.868
AND KILLS HIM, NOT RICKFORD.

29:08.868 --> 29:10.870
AND THEN TWO DAYS LATER,
HICKS KILLS HIMSELF?

29:10.870 --> 29:12.421
IT'S TOO CLEAN.

29:12.421 --> 29:13.963
WE NEED TO
KEEP AFTER RICKFORD.

29:13.963 --> 29:15.965
HE COULD HAVE
KILLED HICKS WITH AN OVERDOSE

29:15.965 --> 29:17.967
AND THEN POSTED
THIS PHONY STATUS UPDATE.

29:17.967 --> 29:20.930
KATE, DON'T YOU THINK
IN THIS CASE

29:20.930 --> 29:23.092
THE SIMPLER EXPLANATION
IS PROBABLY MORE --

29:23.092 --> 29:24.593
OH, COME ON, DANIEL.

29:24.593 --> 29:26.225
HOW MANY TIMES
HAVE I GONE ALONG

29:26.225 --> 29:27.937
WITH ONE OF YOUR CRAZY
CONSPIRACY THEORIES?

29:27.937 --> 29:30.229
DON'T YOU THINK YOU OWE ME
AT LEAST ONE?

29:31.981 --> 29:34.603
WE DROPPED THE CHARGES
AGAINST KENDRA. WHAT
MORE DO YOU WANT?

29:34.603 --> 29:36.605
WARRANT TO TAP
RICKFORD'S PHONE.

29:36.605 --> 29:38.397
I CAN'T SAY IT
ANY MORE PLAINLY.

29:38.397 --> 29:39.989
THE CASE IS CLOSED.

29:39.989 --> 29:41.700
THE JUNKIE CONFESSED.

29:41.700 --> 29:45.324
Colonel: SORRY, DOC.
I HAD A WEEKEND PASS IN OKINAWA.

29:45.324 --> 29:47.076
THIS CUTE LITTLE GEISHA GAL

29:47.076 --> 29:49.038
GAVE ME
A NASTY CASE OF THE CLAP.

29:49.038 --> 29:50.789
OW!

29:50.789 --> 29:54.673
THAT'S WHAT I GET FOR SKIPPING
THE V.D.-PREVENTION FILMS.

29:54.673 --> 29:56.295
VENEREAL DISEASE.

29:56.295 --> 29:57.296
DANIEL?

29:57.296 --> 30:00.589
THINK ABOUT IT.

30:00.589 --> 30:02.421
IF EVERYTHING KENDRA AND
HER HUSBAND TOLD US IS TRUE --

30:02.421 --> 30:04.633
IF THEY WERE BOTH VIRGINS
WHEN THEY GOT MARRIED

30:04.633 --> 30:05.925
AND NEITHER ONE OF THEM
HAD SEX WITH ANYONE ELSE

30:05.925 --> 30:07.636
UNTIL KENDRA GOT RAPED,

30:07.636 --> 30:09.598
THEN SHE MUST HAVE CONTRACTED
HERPES FROM HER RAPIST.

30:09.598 --> 30:11.640
OKAY?
NUCLEOTIDE SEQUENCING

30:11.640 --> 30:13.232
CAN TELL
IF TWO PEOPLE ARE INFECTED

30:13.232 --> 30:14.813
WITH THE SAME
STRAIN OF HERPES.

30:14.813 --> 30:16.695
IT CAN EVEN TELL US
WHO'S BEEN INFECTED LONGER.

30:16.695 --> 30:19.738
WHO GAVE THE DISEASE
TO WHOM.
YES.

30:19.738 --> 30:22.942
THAT'S INTERESTING,
BUT I DON'T THINK WE CAN USE IT.

30:22.942 --> 30:26.205
KENDRA WAS RAPED
UNDER MILITARY JURISDICTION.

30:26.205 --> 30:28.447
WE CAN'T PROSECUTE RICKFORD
FOR THAT CRIME.

30:28.447 --> 30:29.869
PLUS HE WOULD
PROBABLY JUST CLAIM

30:29.869 --> 30:31.120
THAT
THE SEX WAS CONSENSUAL.

30:31.120 --> 30:32.501
Donnie:
HANG ON A SECOND.

30:32.501 --> 30:34.003
WHEN YOU
TALKED TO RICKFORD,

30:34.003 --> 30:36.165
HE DENIED EVER
HAVING SEX WITH KENDRA, RIGHT?

30:36.165 --> 30:37.666
THAT'S WHAT YOU PUT
IN YOUR REPORT.

30:37.666 --> 30:41.340
HE MADE A FALSE STATEMENT
TO A FEDERAL AGENT.

30:41.340 --> 30:43.722
PUNISHABLE BY
UP TO FIVE YEARS IN PRISON.

30:43.722 --> 30:45.514
WAIT -- WAIT A MINUTE --
ARE YOU SUGGESTING
THAT WE PROSECUTE

30:45.514 --> 30:48.057
A RAPIST AND A POSSIBLE
DOUBLE MURDERER FOR LYING?

30:48.057 --> 30:50.349
WHEN THEY COULDN'T PIN
A MURDER CHARGE ON AL CAPONE,

30:50.349 --> 30:52.731
THE TREASURY DEPARTMENT
PUT HIM AWAY FOR TAX EVASION.

30:52.731 --> 30:54.974
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, SLOW DOWN,
ELIOT NESS.

30:55.854 --> 30:58.147
WE'RE GOING TO NEED
A BLOOD ORDER FIRST.

30:58.147 --> 31:00.479
[ TELEPHONE DIALING ]

31:04.984 --> 31:06.695
OH, WHAT THE HELL
IS THIS?

31:06.695 --> 31:07.947
THIS IS A COURT ORDER

31:07.947 --> 31:09.828
REQUIRING YOU
TO SUBMIT TO A BLOOD TEST.

31:11.540 --> 31:12.701
ROLL UP YOUR SLEEVE,
PLEASE.

31:12.701 --> 31:13.872
[ SCOFFS ]

31:13.872 --> 31:15.044
YOU'RE NOT TAKING
MY BLOOD.

31:15.044 --> 31:16.585
KIND OF HOPED
YOU'D SAY THAT.

31:16.585 --> 31:20.589
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST
FOR CONTEMPT OF COURT.

31:20.589 --> 31:23.052
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

31:23.052 --> 31:25.174
ANYTHING YOU SAY
MAY BE USED AGAINST YOU

31:25.174 --> 31:26.845
IN A COURT OF LAW.
CALL MY ATTORNEY.

31:26.845 --> 31:28.057
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY.

31:28.057 --> 31:29.638
[ CHUCKLES ]
AND MY FATHER.

31:29.638 --> 31:31.060
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT TO HAVE
THAT ATTORNEY PRESENT

31:31.060 --> 31:32.351
DURING ANY QUESTIONING.

31:32.351 --> 31:34.813
YOUR HONOR,
THIS BLOOD TEST

31:34.813 --> 31:36.725
WILL CONFIRM THAT
THERE WAS SEXUAL CONTACT

31:36.725 --> 31:38.567
BETWEEN BLAKE RICKFORD
AND KENDRA MURPHY --

31:38.567 --> 31:40.279
A FACT THAT HE DENIED
ON THE RECORD

31:40.279 --> 31:41.690
TO A FEDERAL AGENT,

31:41.690 --> 31:44.023
WHICH, I DON'T HAVE TO TELL YOU,
IS A FELONY.

31:44.023 --> 31:45.404
Larson:
YOUR HONOR, MR. RYAN

31:45.404 --> 31:47.326
IS CONVENIENTLY
LEAVING OUT THE FACT

31:47.326 --> 31:49.578
THAT THE FEDERAL AGENT IN
QUESTION IS HIS OWN EX-WIFE.

31:49.578 --> 31:51.200
HOW IS THAT RELEVANT?

31:51.200 --> 31:53.412
AGENT MORETTI HAS BEEN ON
A WITCH HUNT AGAINST MY CLIENT.

31:53.412 --> 31:55.414
SHE'S ACCUSED MR. RICKFORD
OF MURDER

31:55.414 --> 31:57.586
WITHOUT ANY EVIDENCE TO SUPPORT
SUCH AN OUTRAGEOUS CLAIM.

31:57.586 --> 31:59.959
YOUR HONOR --
YOU SHOULD ALSO BE AWARE

31:59.959 --> 32:02.591
THAT MR. RYAN DELIBERATELY
WITHHELD PERTINENT INFORMATION

32:02.591 --> 32:05.214
ABOUT THE MENTAL HEALTH
OF THIS SO-CALLED VICTIM

32:05.214 --> 32:06.545
WHEN HE OBTAINED
THE BLOOD ORDER.

32:06.545 --> 32:08.307
WHAT'S THIS?

32:08.307 --> 32:11.430
FINDINGS FROM MR. RYAN'S
OWN MEDICAL EXPERT.

32:11.430 --> 32:15.104
THE POOR WOMAN SUFFERS FROM
A NEUROLOGICAL DISORDER --

32:15.104 --> 32:16.725
KLUVER-BUCY SYNDROME --

32:16.725 --> 32:20.649
WHICH LISTS AMONG ITS SYMPTOMS
EMOTIONAL VOLATILITY

32:20.649 --> 32:23.522
AND AN INSATIABLE
SEX DRIVE.

32:33.072 --> 32:34.073
EXCELLENT WORK, PHIL.

32:38.167 --> 32:40.669
NICE TRY, BITCH.

32:42.671 --> 32:46.175
SO, THE BAD GUYS ARE
HAMMERING US WITH THEIR AKs,

32:46.175 --> 32:48.177
AND I'M IN THE TURRET,
JUST WAITING FOR THEM TO POP UP,

32:48.177 --> 32:50.969
TAKE THEIR SHOT,
AND WHEN THEY DO -- BAM!

32:50.969 --> 32:52.851
I PUNCH THEM
WITH THE M240.

32:52.851 --> 32:54.303
IT'S JUST LIKE
PLAYING WHACK-A-MOLE.

32:54.303 --> 32:55.644
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

32:55.644 --> 32:58.647
THAT'S NOT
THE WAY I HEARD IT.

32:58.647 --> 33:01.190
YEAH, I BELIEVE IT WAS ACTUALLY
SPECIALIST MURPHY

33:01.190 --> 33:04.363
WHO TOOK OVER THE M240
WHILE YOU WERE IN THE BACKSEAT

33:04.363 --> 33:06.985
WETTING YOURSELF
LIKE A CANDY-ASS BITCH.

33:06.985 --> 33:09.028
EXCUSE ME.
WHO ARE YOU?

33:09.028 --> 33:11.370
OH, I'M JUST SOMEONE
PERFORMING A PUBLIC SERVICE,

33:11.370 --> 33:13.992
AND THIS GUY
IS NOT ONLY A COWARD,

33:13.992 --> 33:16.575
HE'S ALSO THE SUSPECT
IN THE RAPE OF ONE SOLDIER

33:16.575 --> 33:18.287
AND THE MURDER
OF TWO OTHERS.

33:18.287 --> 33:19.538
COME ON.
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

33:19.538 --> 33:21.670
AND WORD ON THE STREET
IS...

33:21.670 --> 33:23.422
he's got a bad case
of herpes.

33:23.422 --> 33:26.255
I GOT TO GO.

33:30.839 --> 33:33.552
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHO YOU'RE SCREWING WITH.

33:35.264 --> 33:37.516
YOU'RE GOING TO SLIP UP,
BLAKEY BOY.

33:37.516 --> 33:39.768
AND WHEN YOU DO,

33:39.768 --> 33:41.980
I WILL BE THERE
TO TAKE YOU DOWN.

33:47.816 --> 33:49.358
SCOTCH ROCKS.

33:49.358 --> 33:51.280
Daniel: THERE'S A DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN A CONDUCTOR

33:51.280 --> 33:53.362
AND A GUY
JUST WAVING A STICK AROUND.

33:53.362 --> 33:55.574
I MEAN, RICCARDO MUTI
IS A MAESTRO.
MM-HMM.

33:55.574 --> 33:57.206
WHEN DID YOU EVER
SEE MUTI PERFORM?

33:57.206 --> 34:00.579
YOU SAID THAT YOU HAD NOT
BEEN TO A SYMPHONY IN YEARS.

34:00.579 --> 34:01.920
PUBLIC PERFORMANCE.

34:01.920 --> 34:04.213
BUT A FORMER STUDENT
WHO PLAYS SECOND OBOE

34:04.213 --> 34:06.004
GOT ME INTO
A PRIVATE REHEARSAL.

34:06.004 --> 34:08.257
IT WAS INCREDIBLE.
IT WAS INCREDIBLE.

34:08.257 --> 34:10.759
IT WAS THE ENTIRE ORCHESTRA
PLAYING JUST FOR ME.

34:10.759 --> 34:12.341
IT WAS...

34:12.341 --> 34:15.053
ONE OF
THE MOST SUBLIME MOMENTS.

34:27.776 --> 34:31.530
SO, I TALKED TO
MY MOM AND DAD.

34:31.530 --> 34:36.615
AND THEY THINK
I SHOULD TAKE THE TRANSFER.

34:36.615 --> 34:38.827
BUT I'M NOT.

34:38.827 --> 34:39.828
I'M STAYING.

34:39.828 --> 34:41.750
ARE YOU CRAZY?

34:41.750 --> 34:44.583
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE HAPPY.

34:44.583 --> 34:46.585
WELL, I-I'M NOT.

34:46.585 --> 34:48.377
YOU'RE WAY TOO INTO ME.

34:48.377 --> 34:50.088
I-I CAN'T DO THIS ANYMORE.

34:50.088 --> 34:51.920
WAIT, ARE YOU
BREAKING UP WITH ME?

34:51.920 --> 34:54.263
I'M TOO YOUNG TO BE
TIED DOWN TO ONE GIRL.

34:54.263 --> 34:56.265
LOOK, I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

34:56.265 --> 34:58.517
YOU'RE BREAKING UP
WITH ME

34:58.517 --> 35:01.520
SO THAT I'LL GO TO VIENNA,
AREN'T YOU?

35:01.520 --> 35:03.682
YOU JUST DON'T WANT ME
TO LOSE THIS OPPORTUNITY.

35:03.682 --> 35:06.605
THINK WHATEVER YOU WANT.
WE'RE DONE.

35:16.034 --> 35:17.786
[ GROANS ]

35:17.786 --> 35:19.448
I'M SORRY.
I CAN'T DO THIS.

35:19.448 --> 35:21.200
WHAT'S WRONG?

35:22.791 --> 35:24.543
DOES THIS HAVE SOMETHING
TO DO WITH YOUR DIAGNOSIS?

35:24.543 --> 35:26.455
BECAUSE IF YOU THINK
IT MAKES ANY DIFFERENCE

35:26.455 --> 35:27.416
IN HOW I FEEL ABOUT YOU --

35:27.416 --> 35:29.007
NO, NO. IT'S NOT --

35:29.007 --> 35:32.090
IT'S NOT MY ILLNESS --
NOT -- NOT EXACTLY.

35:32.090 --> 35:34.633
TALK TO ME, D.J.

35:34.633 --> 35:36.385
PLEASE.

35:36.385 --> 35:39.968
[ SIGHS ]
NO, YOU -- YOU SHOULD GO.

35:39.968 --> 35:42.971
OKAY.

35:42.971 --> 35:45.854
YOU KNOW, I THOUGHT
YOU'D CHANGED, BUT, UM...

35:45.854 --> 35:48.066
APPARENTLY, NOT SO MUCH.

35:54.983 --> 35:57.906
[ DOOR OPENS, SLAMS ]

36:00.539 --> 36:01.660
AGENT MORETTI.

36:01.660 --> 36:03.622
UNIT CHIEF CONNAGHAN,

36:03.622 --> 36:05.624
OFFICE OF
PROFESSIONAL RESPONSIBILITY.

36:06.915 --> 36:08.166
WE NEED TO TALK.

36:08.166 --> 36:10.249
[ SIGHS ]

36:14.293 --> 36:15.794
I UNDERSTAND
YOU HAD A CONFRONTATION

36:15.794 --> 36:17.256
WITH BLAKE RICKFORD

36:17.256 --> 36:19.758
IN THE LOUNGE OF
THE EMISSARY HOTEL LAST NIGHT.

36:19.758 --> 36:22.801
I WOULD CHARACTERIZE IT
AS MORE OF A CONVERSATION.

36:22.801 --> 36:24.263
YOU FOLLOWED HIM
TO THE BAR.

36:24.263 --> 36:25.804
I WAS TRAILING A SUSPECT.

36:25.804 --> 36:28.647
AS FAR AS I'M AWARE,
MR. RICKFORD ISN'T A SUSPECT

36:28.647 --> 36:30.689
IN ANY CURRENT
FBI INVESTIGATION.

36:30.689 --> 36:33.942
HE CLAIMS THAT YOU
HARASSED AND INTIMIDATED HIM --

36:33.942 --> 36:36.815
THAT YOU SAID
YOU WOULD TAKE HIM DOWN.

36:36.815 --> 36:38.156
IS THAT ACCURATE?

36:38.156 --> 36:39.578
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

36:39.578 --> 36:41.580
AGENT MORETTI,
YOUR ACTIONS DEMONSTRATE

36:41.580 --> 36:43.782
CONDUCT UNBECOMING
AN AGENT OF THIS BUREAU.

36:43.782 --> 36:45.704
YOUR SECURITY CLEARANCE
IS SUSPENDED.

36:45.704 --> 36:47.035
SIR, I HAVE DONE NOTHING

36:47.035 --> 36:49.037
TO WARRANT
THIS TYPE OF PUNISHMENT.

36:49.037 --> 36:51.380
SURRENDER
YOUR SIDEARM AND BADGE.

36:51.380 --> 36:53.382
[ SCOFFS ]

36:53.382 --> 36:57.005
OLD BOYS' NETWORK
CLOSES RANKS AGAIN.

36:57.005 --> 36:58.467
SECURITY CHIEF WALSH,

36:58.467 --> 37:00.299
PLEASE ESCORT AGENT MORETTI
FROM THE BUILDING.

37:12.651 --> 37:15.113
This is Kate.
Leave a message.

37:15.113 --> 37:16.114
[ Answering machine beeps ]

37:16.114 --> 37:17.235
HEY, IT'S ME...

37:17.235 --> 37:18.947
again.

37:18.947 --> 37:20.529
Probably tired of
listening to these messages.

37:20.529 --> 37:22.661
Frankly,
I'm tired of leaving them.

37:22.661 --> 37:24.913
But it's been three days since
I've heard from you, so...

37:24.913 --> 37:26.455
GIVE ME A CALL, PLEASE.

37:26.455 --> 37:28.206
I NEED TO KNOW
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

37:39.758 --> 37:41.720
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

37:51.650 --> 37:53.562
HEY, THERE.
CAN I BUY YOU A DRINK?

38:26.054 --> 38:27.386
DOC.

38:27.386 --> 38:28.727
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

38:28.727 --> 38:30.098
KATE'S A GROWN-UP.

38:30.098 --> 38:32.060
SHE HAS THE RIGHT
NOT TO TALK TO YOU.

38:32.060 --> 38:32.981
[ SIGHS ]

38:38.487 --> 38:40.238
[ CELLPHONE BUZZING ]

39:04.593 --> 39:06.054
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

39:14.853 --> 39:16.855
I JUST WENT BY
KATE'S PLACE,

39:16.855 --> 39:18.437
AND SHE WASN'T HOME.

39:18.437 --> 39:19.648
YOU HEARD FROM HER?

39:19.648 --> 39:21.189
NO, SHE'S NOT
RETURNING MY CALLS.

39:21.189 --> 39:22.781
MINE EITHER.

39:22.781 --> 39:25.033
OKAY, IF YOU GUYS
REALLY WANT TO FIND HER,

39:25.033 --> 39:27.446
YOU CAN TRY
"FOLLOW MY PHONE."
FOLLOW MY WHAT?

39:27.446 --> 39:29.618
IT'S AN APP THAT LETS YOU
TRACK A PHONE IF IT'S LOST.

39:29.618 --> 39:31.750
PEOPLE WONDER WHY
I DON'T CARRY A CELLPHONE.

39:31.750 --> 39:33.492
WELL, SOMETIMES
BIG BROTHER COMES IN HANDY.

39:33.492 --> 39:35.203
LET'S DO IT.
COME ON.

39:35.203 --> 39:37.876
LOOK, ALL I'LL NEED
IS HER CELL PASSWORD.

39:37.876 --> 39:40.959
UH...
TRY VERONICA622.

39:40.959 --> 39:43.211
IT'S HER CAT'S NAME
AND HER BIRTHDAY.

39:43.211 --> 39:45.764
WHAT?
WE WERE MARRIED.

39:45.764 --> 39:47.426
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

39:47.426 --> 39:48.136
[ BEEPS ]

39:48.136 --> 39:49.508
OKAY, I'M IN.

39:49.508 --> 39:52.100
SHE'S GOING SOUTH
ON VETERANS MEMORIAL.

39:52.100 --> 39:55.313
HERE.
CALL ME WITH ANY UPDATES.

39:55.313 --> 39:58.016
YOU SURE YOU WANT TO COME?
KATE'S GONNA BE PISSED.

39:58.016 --> 39:59.438
YEAH?
LET HER BE PISSED.

40:28.637 --> 40:30.428
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

40:30.428 --> 40:33.011
YEAH.
MAX: Kate stopped on a street
in Glen Ellyn.

40:33.011 --> 40:35.684
UH, 1764 CRESCENT.

40:35.684 --> 40:37.556
THANKS, MAX.
And, guys,

40:37.556 --> 40:39.147
I just Googled the address.

40:39.147 --> 40:40.979
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA GUESS
WHO LIVES THERE.

40:58.206 --> 40:59.377
WHERE THE HELL IS SHE?

40:59.377 --> 41:00.749
[ GUNSHOTS ]

41:23.061 --> 41:27.235
KATE?
[ PANTING ]

41:27.235 --> 41:29.237
I HAD TO DO IT.
